Worlddata AI 4

Colaberry has linked in with WorldData.AI , a website that uses Artificial Intelligence to gather all different types of data sets all over the internet, to give you access to all the Industry datasets you need to build the best models and dashboards.  Create an account on www.worlddata.ai.



You now have a basic account.  To get access  to all datasets, go to your profile page and enter "ColaberryWD2021" for the Secret Key.  Click the Submit button and then the Save button.  If they key goes away, that's fine.  Log out and log back in and now you will have partnership access.





The world's data is now at your fingertips.  What are you going to do with it?

If you use this data in your project, you must add the logo somewhere in your work.




You can search for better logo's if need be.  This is our agreement.  We get priority level access, but we must credit them as your Data Source so put their logo a few places throughout documentation.
